                                                Welcome to our institution Arni University which signifies the first ray of the rising sun. It is a matter of sheer pride and joy to state that our University is situated in a pristine location surrounded by amazing scenic natural beauty representing the serene state of Himachal Pradesh. The bank of outrageously beautiful Beas River amidst green Forests is a wonderful backdrop for our campus.</p>
                                                <p>While at Arni University, students gain in-depth knowledge, oratorical deftness and discreet discourse related traits which are considered as vital in today’s chaotic times and competitive world. Our decisions are rooted in dedication and commitment to academic integrity. We aspire to provide all the resources required to team up, lead, and engage our students in global research and practice. On the other hand, the enormous recreational activities at the campus enable the students to develop a healthy balance between their academic and leisure life. There is always a steady tinge of creativity, enthusiasm and joy on our campus.</p>
                                                <p>On the other hand, Faculty at our University is a community of highly committed teachers whose efforts expand the boundaries of knowledge and imagination, and prepares students for wide-ranging careers and lifelong learning. At our university, we are running different schools including Technology, Life Science, Physical Science, Commerce and Management, Pharmacy, Hotel Management, Arts and Humanities, Computer Science and Application; and Skill Development and Vocational Studies.</p>
                                                <p>At Arni, we are revitalizing and elucidating the University’s strategic vision, which will make certain that our University remains determined of:</p>
                                                <p>Newly approved and diverse courses for different schools. </p>
                                                <p>Faculty empowerment through research and technological innovations.</p>
                                                <p>Assisting faculty in discovering novel directions and ambitions.</p>
                                                <p>International collaborations and tie ups with top-notch institutions for the betterment and development of the faculty as well as students.</p>
                                                <p>Finalizing global student exchange programs. </p>
                                                <p>It has been rightly said by the eminent philosopher William James-“The great use of life is to spend it for something that will outlast it.” As Dean (Academic Affairs), I value our time together as a team and I shall always continue to be grateful for the kind concern, generosity, joyful spirit and care expressed by our faculty, staff, and students amid the pandemic. I am a firm believer that our happiness depends largely from living our lives in a consistent approach of eternal generosity. Therefore, I would conclude here that it is my vision to transform students into good human beings and civilized nationals. Let us make the world a better place. Stay Tuned! To emerge as better persons and leaders, I wish you Godspeed.</p>
