                                                The Arni University, Himachal Pradesh has envisioned itself to become a well-known name in Research and Development (R&D) activities. The University’s research program is built to explore the interdisciplinary potential of the faculty and researchers especially with respect to industry and societal aspect of Himachal Pradesh and nearby areas.</p>
                                                <p>Our researchers explore individually and collaboratively a vast array of disciplinary and interdisciplinary research at the cutting edge of science, engineering, and management, Arts and Humanities. Our faculty members' excellence in research is proved by the quality of peer-reviewed articles and conference presentations. All the Departments are equipped with the required infrastructure and other facilities for achieving the goals.</p>
                                                <p>The University has received funding from ICMR, NITI Aayog, and many other agencies of a national repute for Conferences and other research projects. The University is looking forward to signing MOU and research collaborations with government laboratories, Private Universities, industry in India and around the Globe. In Past, many students from the University had completed their Ph.D. and M.Phil research and are doing well in their receptive field of research in Private as well as Government sector.</p>
                                                <p>The office of Dean Research and development supports the research efforts of all the faculty members in the University and provides mentoring to the faculty and researchers, facilitates and built fosters partnerships and collaborations, in their a defined area of research. We are growing every day in research with limited resources and knocking the door of Government funding agencies.</p>
                                                <p>As a Dean of Research at Arni University, I welcome all the budding researcher to join us for your research journey to accomplish excellence in your career.</p>
